examples.en: They submitted their report to us.
Requests must be submitted in writing.
The lawyers submitted the material to the court.
He submitted an application for admission to the school.
The bill will be submitted for approval by Congress.
The president submitted the annual budget to Congress.
His works were submitted for qualification to his denouncer.
He submitted his resignation as of next month.
She submitted her scholarship application tardily, so she was not considered.
The matter should be submitted to the accounts committee in the usual manner.
We submitted a request that more lights be / should be installed on our street.
They vailed their standards and colours, as a sign that they submitted to the discretion of the sultan.
